videos.headline: Stanford not tricked on TCU fake punt
videos.description: TCU punter Adam Nunez takes off running, but Stanford's Brandon Simmons sheds a blocker to make an open-field tackle.

videos.headline: Stanford intercepts Hill on cross-field throw
videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill rolls right and throws the ball to the middle of the field where it is intercepted by Frank Buncom.

videos.headline: Love loses helmet, battles for TD
videos.description: Stanford's star running back Bryce Love showcases his strength dragging the TCU defense across the goal line on his 15-yard touchdown rumble.

videos.headline: Hill connects on deep ball setting up TCU FG
videos.description: Kenny Hill throws it deep for Jalen Reagor who comes back to the ball to make the 42-yard reception.

videos.headline: Love reaches 2,000 yard mark
videos.description: On this 21-yard-run, Stanford's Bryce Love reaches 2,000 rushing yards on the season.

videos.headline: Costello delivers beautiful pass for Stanford TD
videos.description: K.J. Costello finds JJ Arcega-Whiteside in the back corner of the end zone for the 18-yard score as Stanford leads 14-3.

videos.headline: TCU trick return wiped out by penalty
videos.description: TCU's Jalen Reagor lies down in the end zone blending in with the purple background and the lateral to him later in the play is declared a forward pass.

videos.headline: TCU intercepts Stanford attempt downfield
videos.description: Stanford's K.J. Costello takes a chance downfield but his overthrow is intercepted by Nick Orr in the end zone.

videos.headline: Love passes McCaffrey as Stanford's single season rushing leader
videos.description: Bryce Love eclipses Christian McCaffrey's single season rushing mark of 2,019 yards in 2015 on this 10-yard run.

videos.headline: Arcega-Whiteside boxes out TCU defender for second TD
videos.description: K.J. Costello drops back and finds JJ Arcega-Whiteside who boxes out his defender for the catch and dives for his second score.

videos.headline: Hill scrambles for TCU score
videos.description: Kenny Hill can't find anyone open and turns on the jets to reach the pylon for the 6-yard score.

videos.headline: Stanford ends first half with Hail Mary INT
videos.description: Kenny Hill throws up a prayer to the end zone, but the pass is deflected and then intercepted by Frank Buncom to end the first half as Stanford leads 21-10.

videos.headline: Stanford looks to keep TCU off the edge in second half
videos.description: Head coach Brian Shaw says that Stanford's defense has to keep Kenny Hill off the edge when he takes off and scrambles.

videos.headline: Stanford in command
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws two touchdowns to JJ Arcega-Whiteside, and Bryce Love passes Christian McCaffrey for most rushing yards in team history as Stanford leads TCU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Stanford in command) 2017/12/28 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: TCU scores on pass back to Hill
videos.description: Kenny Hill throws a backwards pass to Desmon White who throws it back to Hill who runs it in for the touchdown as TCU trails 21-16.

videos.headline: Love explodes for 69-yard Stanford TD
videos.description: Bryce Love follows his blockers up the middle and finds a crease to take it 69 yards to the house as Stanford leads 28-16.

videos.headline: Hill buys time in pocket, fires TD strike
videos.description: TCU's Kenny Hill roams the pocket and fires a pass to Desmon White in the end zone for the 11-yard score to cut the deficit to 28-23.

videos.headline: Stanford strips TCU receiver and recovers
videos.description: TCU's Desmon White fights for extra yards when the ball is stripped by Stanford's Malik Antoine and recovered by Frank Buncom.

videos.headline: Reagor burns Stanford defense on 93-yard TD
videos.description: Kenny Hill throws a beautiful pass to Jalen Reagor who beats his defender and catches the ball in stride for the 93-yard score.

videos.headline: TCU takes lead on electric punt return
videos.description: TCU's Desmon White catches the punt facing his own end zone, but turns back toward the sideline and sprints up field for the 76-yard score on the return as TCU takes the lead.

videos.headline: Arcega-Whiteside's 3rd TD gives Stanford lead
videos.description: K.J. Costello throws it up for JJ Arcega-Whiteside who makes the catch in the end zone as Stanford takes a 37-36 lead.

videos.headline: Love exits game with thumb injury
videos.description: Bryce Love leaves the game and heads to the tent to have his thumb examined and has yet to return to the game late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: TCU snags INT to secure win
videos.description: TCU's Innis Gaines intercepts K.J. Costello's pass over the middle to give TCU the ball back late with the lead.

videos.headline: Big plays from TCU lead to upset of Stanford
videos.description: The Horn Frogs erase an 18-point deficit with the help of a 93-yard rout and a 76-yard punt return to defeat Stanford.

videos.headline: TCU's huge second-half earns Alamo Bowl win
videos.description: Bryce Love racks up 145 yards and two touchdowns for Stanford but TCU rallies behind the efforts of Desmon White and Kenny Hill to take a 39-37 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (TCU's huge second-half earns Alamo Bowl win) 2017/12/28 ESHEET
